Package org.github.terminological.jepidemic.estimate

Class CoriTimeseriesEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.github.terminological.jepidemic.estimate.CoriTimeseriesEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<CoriTimeseriesEntry>, TimeseriesEntry

    public class CoriTimeseriesEntry
extends Object
implements TimeseriesEntry, Comparable<CoriTimeseriesEntry>
    A timeseries entry in a ordered straucture with accessors for the previous and next items in the time series.
    This is where the component calculations for the Cori method are performed. The calculations for the cori method are not performed until the recache() method is called, which is done by the CoriEstimator::estimateForProfile method when considering a new infectivity profile.
